sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client
    participant LLS as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant Inline as Ragas Inline Provider<br/>(in-process)
    participant Ragas as Ragas evaluate()<br/>(asyncio.to_thread)
    participant InfAPI as Inference API<br/>(in-process)

    rect rgb(220, 240, 255)
        Note over Client,InfAPI: Flow 1: Inline Evaluation
        Client->>LLS: POST /alpha/eval/run-eval<br/>HTTP/8321
        LLS->>Inline: route to inline::trustyai_ragas
        Inline->>Inline: Load dataset via DatasetIO API
        Inline->>Ragas: asyncio.to_thread(evaluate)<br/>max_workers=1
        Ragas->>InfAPI: LLM completions<br/>(LlamaStackInlineLLM wrapper)
        InfAPI-->>Ragas: completion response
        Ragas->>InfAPI: Embeddings<br/>(LlamaStackInlineEmbeddings wrapper)
        InfAPI-->>Ragas: embedding vectors
        Note over Ragas: Compute metrics:<br/>answer_relevancy, context_precision,<br/>faithfulness, context_recall
        Ragas-->>Inline: EvalResult
        Inline-->>LLS: evaluation results
        LLS-->>Client: JSON response
    end

    participant Remote as Ragas Remote Provider<br/>(in-process)
    participant KFP as Kubeflow Pipelines API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Pod1 as KFP Pod: retrieve_data<br/>(ephemeral)
    participant Pod2 as KFP Pod: run_ragas<br/>(ephemeral)
    participant S3 as S3 Object Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    rect rgb(255, 240, 220)
        Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: Remote Evaluation (Kubeflow Pipelines)
        Client->>LLS: POST /alpha/eval/run-eval<br/>HTTP/8321
        LLS->>Remote: route to remote::trustyai_ragas
        Remote->>Remote: Resolve base image<br/>(env var → ConfigMap → default)
        Remote->>KFP: create_run_from_pipeline_func<br/>HTTPS/443 Bearer Token
        KFP-->>Remote: run_id
        Remote-->>LLS: job_id (async)
        LLS-->>Client: job_id

        Note over KFP,S3: Pipeline execution (async)
        KFP->>Pod1: Schedule retrieve_data
        Pod1->>LLS: GET datasets<br/>HTTP/8321
        LLS-->>Pod1: dataset rows
        Pod1-->>KFP: dataset artifact

        KFP->>Pod2: Schedule run_ragas
        Pod2->>LLS: LLM + Embedding inference<br/>HTTP/8321
        LLS-->>Pod2: inference responses
        Note over Pod2: Ragas evaluate()
        Pod2->>S3: PUT results.jsonl<br/>HTTPS/443 AWS IAM
        Pod2-->>KFP: complete

        Client->>LLS: GET /alpha/eval/job-status<br/>HTTP/8321
        LLS->>Remote: check status
        Remote->>KFP: get run status<br/>HTTPS/443 Bearer Token
        KFP-->>Remote: SUCCEEDED
        Remote-->>LLS: status

        Client->>LLS: GET /alpha/eval/job-result<br/>HTTP/8321
        LLS->>Remote: get results
        Remote->>S3: GET results.jsonl<br/>HTTPS/443 AWS IAM (s3fs/pandas)
        S3-->>Remote: JSONL data
        Remote-->>LLS: EvalResult
        LLS-->>Client: JSON response
    end
